~~indexes. i have talke about the importance of this subject and the
~~reason behind my choice and about the plan of the research . i also
~~talked shortly in the preface about sheikh alsaady, his writings .in the
~~first section i presented alsaady and his way in making recommendations
~~and advisabilities. i have explained what making preferences mean and
~~its importance and its faces for sheikh alsaady also, i have compared
~~between al sa,dy and mohmmed al amin alshanqiti in making preferences
~~accompamed with evidences and sources in the second section , i
~~presented, in details, al sa,adi,s preferences opinions, evidences,
~~comparing him with what most of explainers have said . i concluded with
~~a summary and a discussion . in my research , i make references of
